*Gubite* se u svojim mislima. (You get lost in your thoughts.)

Vizuelno, *gubite* nešto od svoje lepote. (Visually, you lose some of your beauty.)

Dobijamo ili *gubimo* u životu. (We gain or lose in life.)

Neka se *gubi* u mraku. (Let it be lost in the darkness.)

*Gubiti* nadu je najgori oblik patnje. (To lose hope is the worst form of suffering.)